# Utility and Economic Model

LLM Studio does not operate with a native token; instead, it focuses on delivering direct utility through its subscription-based platform.

## Distribution
No tokens distributed. Access is granted through tiered subscription plans adapted to project size and complexity.

## Utility & Incentives
- Multiple subscription tiers offering tailored automation and support features.
- Early adopters receive discounted plans and prioritized customer service.
- Partnership integrations offer combined value solutions.

## Participation Logic
Users engage through subscriptions based on their operational scope, gaining access to LLM Studioâ€™s comprehensive automation tools.

## Sustainability
Subscription revenues fund continual platform development, security enhancements, and support services, avoiding reliance on token market fluctuations.